# VoIP / SIP — Learn, Build, Break, Drill (Debian 12)

**Distro:** **Debian 12** (`apt`, `systemd`, `nftables`). Ubuntu LTS is ~identical.  
**Reference book:** Carla Schroder, *Linux Networking Cookbook* (O'Reilly) — for Linux networking underneath VoIP. JD↔book map in **§10**.

