## §6 — Maintain

| Area | What you do (Debian) |
|------|----------------------|
| **Patches** | `apt upgrade` in staging; **`needrestart`**; rebuild RTPengine kernel module on **new kernel**. |
| **Config** | `/etc/kamailio`, `/etc/asterisk` in **Git**; `kamailio -c` syntax check; `asterisk -rx 'pjsip show endpoints'`. |
| **Firewall** | `/etc/nftables.conf` in Git; `nft -c -f` dry-run before reload. |
| **Certs** | `openssl x509 -in fullchain.pem -noout -dates` — automate 60-day warning. |
| **Logs** | `journalctl -u kamailio -u asterisk --since '1 hour ago'`; rotate PCAP disk. |

**Change window order:** announce → baseline capture → drain/shift → **one layer** change → `ss` + OPTIONS + test call → go/no-go (rollback criterion written **before** change).

